<h2>Matthew House to host first ever Winterfest!!</h2>
</div>
<p></p>
<p>01.31.15</p>
<div class="newsbody"><p>The Matthew House team has decided that we want to help&nbsp;show our refugee friends that they can not only &quot;survive&quot; Canadian winters, they can THRIVE!!&nbsp; We are therefore holding our first ever WINTERFEST in <strong>Trinity Bellwoods Park</strong> behind our Dundas St. home on <strong>Sunday February 22nd from 2 to 4 pm</strong>.&nbsp; There will be&nbsp; &quot;learn to skate&quot; opportunties, tobaganning, &quot;fun with snow&quot; activities and free hot chocolate!&nbsp;&nbsp;Even&nbsp;our local city councillor Mike Layton&nbsp;( and other celebrities) may make an appearance!</p>
<p>If you happen to have any <strong>used skates </strong>or <strong>helmets</strong> (all sizes) we would be happy to recieve them! &nbsp;Just drop them off at our 981 Dundas St. West location.&nbsp;&nbsp;Thanks and&nbsp;&nbsp;See you at the FEST!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Click here for&nbsp;a&nbsp;short&nbsp;VIDEO re MH&nbsp;Winterfest and SKATES</strong>:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://youtu.be/H_L7Fxu-CfE">http://youtu.be/H_L7Fxu-CfE</a>&nbsp;</p>
